  "detailed_description": "<i><strong>Bombing!!</strong></i> is a <strong>lo-fi graffiti sandbox simulation where every inch of the environment can be used as a canvas</strong>  for your wildest creations. Armed with your trusty backpack, a handful of paint cans and a selection of tools, take to the streets and fill them with your creations!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527520/extras/2d4d2c073a734cd5ac26b0e8ce4a6fbb.poster.avif?t=1683133476\" width=488 height=152 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527520/extras/2d4d2c073a734cd5ac26b0e8ce4a6fbb.webm?t=1683133476\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1527520/extras/2d4d2c073a734cd5ac26b0e8ce4a6fbb.mp4?t=1683133476\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 🏙️ Several atmospheric levels, from rooftops to subways, for you to explore!<br></li><li> 🔨 Vandalize every surface with your creations!<br></li><li> 🎹 Licensed tunes by awesome independent artists to get the inspiration flowing!<br></li><li> 🎨 A wide colour palette of paints, caps and paint pens to help push your imagination to its limits!<br></li><li> 👩🏿‍🎨 Chunky, crunchy art!<br></li><li> 🔦 Other tools to help you in your miscreant endeavors!<br></li><li> And much more!</li></ul>",
